name: Register on the Utest.com page

testSteps.description: Given than Carlos is on the Utest page

children.description: Carlos open up
Carlos opens the Utest page

testSteps.description: When he clicks Join Today on the Utest page

children.description: Carlos join today
Carlos clicks on Click in the button Join Today

testSteps.description:
And he enters the data required in the first registration step
| first_name | last_name | email_address | month_bird | day_bird | year_bird | language |
| Carlos | Castro | ccastrova@tting.com | December | 3 | 1997 | Spanish |

children.description: Carlos enters
Carlos enters 'Carlos' into Where we write the first name
Carlos enters 'Castro' into Where we write the last name
Carlos enters 'ccastrova@tting.com' into Where we write the email address
Carlos select December on Click on the month of date birth
Carlos select 3 on Click on the day of date birth
Carlos select 1997 on Click on the year of date birth
Carlos enters 'Spanish' into Where we write the native language
Carlos types 'ENTER' in Where we write the native language
Carlos clicks on Click on the button for the steps next

testSteps.description:
And he enters the data required in the second registration step
| city | postal_code | country |
| Bello, Antioquia | 050044 | Colombia |

children.description: Carlos enters two
Carlos clicks on Where we write the city
Carlos clears field Where we write the city
Carlos enters 'Bello, Antioquia' into Where we write the city
Carlos types 'DOWN' in Where we write the city
Carlos types 'ENTER' in Where we write the city
Carlos enters '050044' into Where we write the code postal
Carlos clicks on Where we write the country
Carlos enters 'Colombia' into Where we write the country
Carlos types 'ENTER' in Where we write the country
Carlos clicks on Click on the button for the steps next

testSteps.description:
And he enters the data required in the third registration step
| computer | version | language_computer | mobile_device | model | operating_system |
| Windows | Windows 10 Education | Spanish | Motorola | Moto G9 Plus | Android 10 |
